post_content:
Hi All,

I’ve been attempting a collaborative online error set as seen on Instagram under @t206er - I’ve got about 166 different error cards so far and would love any stories and errors that are out there if your willing to share! Just looking for a bio on the card, if any, how long you’ve had the card and images front and back of the card to repost with your consent for the online error collection. Thanks and check out @t206er for a feel of what  I am looking for : misprints, miscuts, multistrike, multiprint, ghosts, wet sheet transfers, underprints, color variations, printer scraps, blank backs, upside down backs, proofs and whatever else you got!
Search net54 for the words ghost and scrape and you will find a lot of threads and bst posts full of examples.
